Illinois Department of Corrections (IDOC)

The Illinois Department of Corrections allows you to search by last name, birth date, or 
inmate number to locate information regarding the status of a single inmate.  
There is no bulk data that is made available.  It is unclear what if any data is collected and what 
is available through Illinoisâ€™ Freedom of Information Act.

Fields available in single inmate search:

Physical Profile
Date of Birth
Weight
Hair
Sex
Height
Race
Eyes

Mars, Scars, & Tattoos

Admission / Release / Discharge Info

Admission Date
Projected Release Date
Last Paroled Date
Projected Discharge Date

Sentencing Information (this is listed for every conviction the individual has)
Mittimus (Case Number)
Class
Count
Offense
Custody Date
Sentence
County 
Sentence Discharged
